{"title":"黎明就在风雨后","authors":["程光锐"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":1,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎明就在风雨后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"程光锐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自由在哪里？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空留下一座自由神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呆站在纽约港口！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民主在哪里？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早随着林肯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"葬入坟墓，化为骷髅！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的人民好，山河秀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的命运握在谁的手？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这锦绣的国土上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反动派要盖监狱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民要起朱楼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昼与夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人与兽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命与反动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新生与腐朽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎明前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一场激烈的搏斗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁窗和电椅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迫害和阴谋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎能挡住历史的潮流！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"君不见，杜波依斯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把白发献给共产主义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这夜最黑的时候。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茫茫夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终究有尽头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷声阵阵天外吼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴雨要来啦，风满楼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那胜利的黎明呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就在几番暴雨狂风后。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}